org.openstack4j.model.image.v2

Interface Task

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Buildable<TaskBuilder>, ModelEntity, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GlanceTask

    public interface Task
extends ModelEntity, Buildable<TaskBuilder>
    An object representing a Glance V2 task. Tasks offer end users a front end to long running asynchronous operations.
    Author:
    emjburns
